title: Looking For Duo Partner (Support)
body:
Currently in placements and not doing the best at the moment (2-2) and so I am currently searching for a duo que partner or partners. I main AD Carry preferably looking for a Support main. Started playing ranked last season and ended up in Silver, would like to push to Gold this season.
Add me if interested

Main:{{champion:67}}  364k Mastery Points

IGN: Jomsu

replies.body: I'll throw my hat in the ring however I do prefer non-meta supports...that being said I seem to be able to make shaco support work, amongst other non-meta picks
